title: GET_TIMECYCLE_MODIFIER_NAME_BY_INDEX
content:
0x28CB8608// GetTimecycleModifierNameByIndex
char* GET_TIMECYCLE_MODIFIER_NAME_BY_INDEX(int modifierIndex);Parameters:modifierIndex: The timecycle modifier index.Returns: The timecycle modifier name.Examples:Lualocal modifierIndex = GetTimecycleModifierIndex()

if modifierIndex ~= -1 then
  local modifierName = GetTimecycleModifierNameByIndex(modifierIndex)
  print("current timecycle name is " .. modifierName)
end
